title: Back in Time* (Snippet)
lyrics:
[Lyrics from snippet]
[Verse 1]
And I still look back on all our conversations
I left you on read so many times
And I wish I never told you that I loved you
But I did
[Chorus]
If I could
Then I’d go back in time
Yeah I would hit rewind
And stop myself from me and you
If I could
If I could I would
I’d make your heart forget
The pain that’s in your head
I’d stop myself from hurting you
If I could
If I could I would
